#Write a python code to generate Personalized Greeting using input/ output statements

INPUT :
    
# Take input from the user for the name
name = input("enter the name : ")

# Take input from the user for the occasion
occasion = input("enter the occasion : ")

# Take input from the user for the greeting message
greet = input("enter the greeting : ")

# Print the message with the occasion and name formatted in the greeting
print(f"Happy {occasion} {name}")

# Print the user-provided greeting
print(f"{greet}")


OUTPUT :

enter the name : utsav
enter the occasion : birthday
enter the greeting : Hope this day comes with lots of joy and happiness in your life
Happy birthday utsav
Hope this day comes with lots of joy and happiness in your life
